1. Install the broker
sudo apt-get install mosquitto
*your mosquitto version may not support websockets
2. Start Server
mosquitto -p 1882
2. Install lib
pip install paho-mqtt
3. Run progs

Installing mosquito server with web support

step 1: install libwebsockets mosquitto 1.4 (WebSockets support)
 - port 9001
http://icanseedeadcats.com/tag/mosquitto/ 

step 2: run mosquitto --> mosquitto -c /etc/mosquitto/mosquitto.conf

step 3: open browser, and console

step 4: run a publisher

Docker mosquitto:
https://hub.docker.com/r/toke/mosquitto/
docker run -ti -p 1883:1883 -p 9001:9001 toke/mosquitto
